---
title: Crumbled BBQ Double Tofu Sandwiches with Creamy and Crunchy Cabbage-Apple Slaw
description: Say hello to bold BBQ flavour in a tofu dish! Crumbled tofu is sprinkled with BBQ seasoning, oven-baked and smothered in a sweet and sticky BBQ sauce to create a show-stopping sandwich filling!
